textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value ENABLED (Enabled|Disabled)
Value PHY_STATUS (up|down)
Value DESCRIPTION (.+)
Value MAC_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value MTU (\d+)
Value IP_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value SUBNET_MASK (\S+)
Value OPER_STATUS (up|down)
Value LAST_CHANGE (.+)

Start
  ^Interface: ${INTERFACE}, ${ENABLED}, Physical link is ${PHY_STATUS}$$
  ^\s+Description: ${DESCRIPTION}$$
  ^\s+MAC address: ${MAC_ADDRESS}, MTU: ${MTU}$$
  ^\s+IP address: ${IP_ADDRESS}, Subnet mask: ${SUBNET_MASK}$$
  ^\s+Operational status: ${OPER_STATUS}$$
  ^\s+Last (link|change) (up|down) at: ${LAST_CHANGE}$$ -> Record
